high_descs: Turn right and walk out of the room then go right and walk to the far end of the kitchen island and pick up the lettuce from the kitchen island.
Pick up the lettuce from the pan on the kitchen island.
Walk forward to the kitchen sink.
Put the lettuce in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the Lettuce in the SinkBasin

high_descs: Turn left and right twice, then turn left and go to the lettuce on the kitchen countertop.
Take the lettuce out of the cabbage.
Move over to the kitchen sink.
Put the lettuce in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Take lettuce out of the cabbage. Move over to the kitchen countertop. Put lettuce in the SinkBasin.

high_descs: Turn right, take left, leave the room, turn right, move forward, turn right, take left towards the counter top.
Take the lettuce from the counter top.
Turn left, move, turn right towards the sink.
Put the lettuce inside the sink.
anns.task_desc: To get the lettuce from the counter top, put inside the sink.
